(* 
bit.ly/下載_鱫鰰macOS開機鰈鱮ISO鯯作_dmg 
GitHub.com/VirgoEros/macOScreateBootInstallUSB/blob/master/AppleScript 

YouTube視頻演示: macOS USB鯯作 
YouTube視頻演示: macOS ISO鯯作 
